Detailed Description

template<typename KEY, typename VALUE, typename PAIR_TRAITS, typename TRAITS, class ALLOCATOR>
template<typename VALUE_REF, typename ITERATOR>
class cds::map::michael_map::details::michael_map_base< KEY, VALUE, PAIR_TRAITS, TRAITS, ALLOCATOR >::NonConcurrentIterator< VALUE_REF, ITERATOR >

Non-concurrent iterator.

This iterator is not thread safe. Template parameter VALUE_REF defines type of iterator return value (const or not) Template parameter ITERATOR defines iterator class of underlined ordered list.
